# Unified VSL Template — Implementation Plan

A complete redesign of all 4 VSL pages (Construction, Restaurant, Real Estate, Tax Resolution) into a cohesive, conversion-optimized template system.

---

## Research Summary

### UX Research & Design Artifacts

#### Desktop + Mobile Wireframe
![Full page wireframe with all labeled sections and mobile side-by-side](/Users/king-lewie/.gemini/antigravity/brain/0945db10-0380-4328-b71e-d9e8674b6c6f/vsl_wireframe_desktop_mobile_1773153479287.png)

#### Heatmap & Attention Analysis
![VSL heatmap with scroll depth data and touchpoint mapping](/Users/king-lewie/.gemini/antigravity/brain/0945db10-0380-4328-b71e-d9e8674b6c6f/vsl_heatmap_attention_1773153513445.png)

**Key data points:**
- 90% of visitors reach the trust bar
- 75% reach pain points
- 60% reach How It Works
- 45% reach testimonials
- 30% reach FAQ
- 20% reach the final CTA

**Implication:** Place the most persuasive content high (before 60% scroll). Strategic placement of 3 CTA moments: after hero, after results, after FAQ.

#### Service Blueprint
![User journey from acquisition through follow-up with emotional arc](/Users/king-lewie/.gemini/antigravity/brain/0945db10-0380-4328-b71e-d9e8674b6c6f/vsl_service_blueprint_1773153528477.png)

**Emotional arc:** Curious → Engaged → Interested → Convinced → Committed → Relieved

#### Dedicated Mobile Wireframe
![Mobile-first detailed wireframe with thumb zones and sticky CTA bar](/Users/king-lewie/.gemini/antigravity/brain/0945db10-0380-4328-b71e-d9e8674b6c6f/vsl_mobile_wireframe_1773153557953.png)

